<br type="automatic_original" />
</title>
</titleBlock>
<titleBlock>
<title>
<sentence type="quasi">作り方</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</title>
</titleBlock>
<list>
<listItem>
<sentence><enclosedCharacter description="○">１</enclosedCharacter>　オクラ、モロヘイヤはさっと塩ゆで<sampling type="end" />にし、ざるに広げて手早く冷ます。</sentence>
